Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,————————————————————- ＯＰ————————————————————\N-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:21.76,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てしない空をゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.86,0:01:25.15,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見えない翼が導く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.26,0:01:27.17,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥か彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:33.91,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}僕らを待つ　まだ見ぬ未来へと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:43.57,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Always　覚め切ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:46.57,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速すぎるthat night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.77,0:01:53.31,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透明な闇に囲まれ　誰も似た輪の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.41,0:01:56.38,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Find you　あの日の風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:01:59.71,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揺れ動いた場所
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:01.04,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal my pass
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:05.99,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全て君に合うためのプロセスだったね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.38,0:02:09.08,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly opened my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.14,0:02:11.51,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need the brightness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.99,0:02:15.45,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方から聞こえる予感に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:19.55,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓動を震わせていたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:23.34,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reality　It's a reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.40,0:02:26.82,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can believe myself for again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:30.22,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光の中 目覚めていく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.27,0:02:33.88,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じてくれた君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:35.08,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:36.32,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never lost my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:39.70,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ここで生まれ変わる景色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:43.28,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷さえ今　誇りになる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:47.89,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}だから君とBurst The Gravity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.09,0:00:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:21.76,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沒有盡頭的天空中行走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.86,0:01:25.15,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由看不見的羽翼引導
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.26,0:01:27.17,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通向遙遠的比方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:33.91,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}那看不見的未來依舊在等待我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:43.57,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Always 不願清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:46.57,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了 that night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.77,0:01:53.31,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那透明的黑暗包圍 誰也逃不出這個圈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.41,0:01:56.38,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Find you 那日的風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:01:59.71,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變幻不定的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:01.04,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal my pass
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:05.99,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都是為了與你相會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.38,0:02:09.08,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly opened my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.14,0:02:11.51,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need the brightness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.99,0:02:15.45,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自彼方聽聞的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:19.55,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我震動鼓舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:23.34,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reality　It's a reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.40,0:02:26.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can believe myself for again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:30.22,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在光的沐浴下 我漸漸清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.27,0:02:33.88,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是你 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:35.08,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:36.32,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never lost my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:39.70,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏不斷變化的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:43.28,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的傷口 是我的驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:47.89,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}因為你和Burst The Gravity
